  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Nigeria ICCO NJR 5- Emergency Resposne to Food Securtiy and Wash Needs in Borno State</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The objective of this project is to provide life-saving Food Security and Livelihood, WASH and Protection services addressing sectoral gaps over a period of 12 months. The food security will involve the provision of livestock, poultry and seed distribution. WASH services include constriction of latrines, boreholes and provision of NFIs. Interventions will also include nutrition and protection (GBV and MHPSS).</narrative>
  </description>
